```plantuml
@startuml
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

interface Invoker {
}

note left of Invoker: 调用者持有命令对象，\n并在某刻调用execute()

interface Command {
    execute()
    undo()
}

note right of Command: 调用命令对象的execute()\n就可以让接收者进行动作

class ConcreteCommand {
    execute()
    undo()
}

note left of ConcreteCommand: 定义了动作和接收者之间的\n绑定关系，调用者只需要\n调用execute()就可以发出请求

interface Receiver {
    action()
}

note right of Receiver: 接收者知道如何实现这个请求

interface Client {
}

note right of Client: 这个客户负责创建一个\nConcreteCommand，并设置其接受者

Invoker --> Command
Client --> ConcreteCommand
Client --> Receiver
Receiver --> ConcreteCommand
ConcreteCommand ..|> Command

@enduml
```
